DAC.Control register comment: 0 = disabled. 5 = 4 to 20 mA, 6 =  0 to 20 mA, 7 = 0 to 24 mA.

Antenna.TriggerDeadtime Comment: Minimum interval between antenna triggers in us

Trigger.TriggerSourceComment: Accelerometer (0-3), Antenna (4), Lemo (8-11), Ethernet/sync (12). 5-7 not used do not change

SDUMessage.BroadcastComment: What index of look-up table to issue now.
SDUMessage.SDU Message Comment: 256 possible SDU responses. 0 = ignore, 1=trigger, 2=start veto, 3=end veto

LEMOOutputs.OutputTypeComment: Select between latched output (0) and pulsed output (1) for LEMO 0 and 1
LEMOOutputs.Output Pulse Lengths Comment: Allowed values are from 0-2550 ns, in increments of 10ns
LEMOOutputs.WriteFrontPanelOutputsComment: A write to bit 0 goes to output 0 and a write to bit 1 goes to output 1

Accelerometer.TriggerDeadtime Comment: Minimum interval between acceleromenter triggers in us

ControlAndStatus.ControlandStatusComment: Bit 0: General Reset of the DRAM pointers. Bit 4: Enable(1)or Disable(0)DRAM writes. Should be set to 16 (0x10) at start of run.
